flowchart TD
  START([dispatch method + path + version]) --> LOAD[load routes\nroute cache → provider on miss]
  LOAD --> MATCH[resolveRoutes\npriority desc · specificity desc · routeId]
  MATCH --> ANY{any match?}
  ANY -->|no| NF[record failed resolution\nGatewayRejected no_route\nthrow RouteNotFoundError]
  ANY -->|yes| INT{route checksum valid?}
  INT -->|no| IErr[record integrityFailure\nGatewayRejected integrity]
  INT -->|yes| AUTH{authRequired?}

  AUTH -->|yes| IDR[Identity.resolve\npropagate context]
  IDR --> AOK{authenticated?}
  AOK -->|no| REJ1[GatewayRejected unauthenticated]
  AOK -->|yes| FF
  AUTH -->|no| FF{feature flag?}

  FF -->|off| REJ2[GatewayRejected feature_disabled]
  FF -->|on / none| POL[Policy.evaluate per policy]
  POL --> PD{any deny?}
  PD -->|yes| REJ3[GatewayRejected policy_denied]
  PD -->|no| RL{rate limit policy?}
  RL -->|consume → blocked| REJ4[GatewayRejected rate_limited]
  RL -->|allowed / none| TGT[target resolution]
  TGT --> DISC{targetService?}
  DISC -->|yes| DR[Service Discovery.resolve → endpoint]
  DISC -->|no| STATIC[static targetEndpoint]
  DR --> PIPE
  STATIC --> PIPE[middleware pipeline in order]
  PIPE --> MOK{middleware ok?}
  MOK -->|missing / error| REJ5[GatewayRejected middleware_*]
  MOK -->|ok| HANDLER[optional upstream handler]
  HANDLER --> TMO{elapsed > timeout?}
  TMO -->|yes| REJ6[GatewayRejected timeout]
  TMO -->|no| DISPATCHED[record latency\nRequestDispatched]
  DISPATCHED --> END([target + params + context + result])
